upnp cp
upnp device

upnp server
 - cp : m-search and gather device list (ssdp server)
  > device added/removed event (ssdp server)
  > get device & service information (http client)	
  > send action invoke (http client)
  > event subscribe management (http server)
 - device : send notify and reponse against m-search (ssdp server)
  > provide device description and scpd (http server)
  > response against action invoke (http server)
  > handle event subscribe management (http server)
